OL,3,GNEWSCBBC Scotland TV and radio
OL,4,Cprogrammes disrupted by fire
OL,5,
OL,6,FBBC Scotland programming on TV and
OL,7,Fradio was disrupted for a time this
OL,8,Fmorning after a fire broke out at the
OL,9,Fbroadcaster's headquarters building at
OL,10,FPacific Quay in Glasgow.
OL,12,FA fire alarm sounded at around 6.30am
OL,13,Fprompting an immediate evacuation of
OL,14,Fthe building.
OL,16,FEmergency services arrived on the scene
OL,17,Fwithin minutes.
OL,19,FThe fire occurred in a plant room at
OL,20,Fthe top of the building. It was
OL,21,Fdiscovered by security staff.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
