OL,5,
OL,6,FStaff were allowed to return to the
OL,7,FPacific Quay building shortly before
OL,8,F8.30am.
OL,10,FBBC Radio Scotland resumed broadcasting
OL,11,Fat 8.35am.
OL,13,FOn television, BBC One Scotland's
OL,14,Fbreakfast news bulletins did not go out
OL,15,Fat 6.55am, 7.30am, 7.55am or 8.25am.
OL,17,FInstead, Scottish viewers received BBC
OL,18,FLondon. The presenter of the London
OL,19,Fprogramme welcomed Scottish viewers at
OL,20,Fthe start of bulletins at 7.30am,
OL,21,F7.55am and 8.25am.
